content.solution_latex:
We can take $A = (0,0,0),$ $B = (1,1,1),$ and $C = (0,0,1).$  Then line is $AB$ is parameterized by $(t,t,t).$

[asy]
import three;

size(180);
currentprojection = perspective(6,3,2);

